{
  "stem": "9590.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, when he was in the kolkhoz, he also used the horses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Two of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Big, beautiful horses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when he left Warkowicze to go, to flee, he also went with the horses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Somebody brought one horse back to us, and told us that my father was killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It happened that he went as far as the border, was a shtetl by the name of Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the border between Poland and Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The border was guarded, and the guard did not let my father cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He remained in Ostrog overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That night the Germans bombed Ostrog and the house where my father was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father was killed, and also one horse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And somehow one horse remained alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The person that came to tell us that, also said that where my father was, after the bombs left, and it was quiet, there was a man that lived in the house by the name of Waldman, and he was guarding the body.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "According to our religion, a dead body is not supposed to be left alone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- somebody has to guard it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Waldman, a strange man, took it upon himself to stay, even though it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The bombs did not cease to be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He stayed overnight with my father's body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he saw to it that the next day somebody will take the horse and bring it to our town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember that instance, when a strange man came with the horse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The horse, though an animal, felt the tragedy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "His head was bent, the eyes closed, and when you looked at that horse, you were able to see that he is also crying for the loss.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
